{"tid":452118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共統戰重點 擬深入港澳台各級學校及社區 更深入台高學府發展組織及朋友圈","createTime":"2017-10-30T01:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T03:52:52.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"729c2bb97b1fc8b5d7a198ef17b759c471731bb2","tid":452118,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:21:42.000Z","msg":"中共統戰重點 擬深入台灣高等學府、發展「朋友圈」<br />\n<br />\n香港《星島日報》報導，尤權現年63歲，主政福建省5年，相當熟悉港澳台事務，據傳這是他被欽點擔任中央統戰部長的主因。<br />\n<br />\n在中共中央統戰部在18大工作報告中指出，指統戰重點目標是青年及精英，將深入到高等教育學府，發展組織，包括校方社團及朋友圈等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">統戰部並指出，在海外策動「反獨」，已有高達100多國和地區成立200多個反「獨」促統組織，更對台灣青年舉辦多項「聯誼活動」，包括夏令營、學生一對一結對民宿等，對港澳則深入到各級學校及社區；累計5年來約有5萬人次參加中國統戰部的研習或培訓。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2237453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2237453&d=UtW9Xjt%2BaK%2Bs9a9qy0N3PqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=85df9a86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2237453&h=37b293c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2237453</a>"},{"pid":"45365703b81e8a56f320490eec19ceb9ca2f0801","tid":452118,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15461cd50c7664b0d3c4c63ac009b38a4bc59033","tid":452118,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a2f53445706dd430178949a2b55d6a1697fc12","tid":452118,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">繼續善用長性人形生化統戰武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmo